<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.2.9">
<l>kākku miyalviṉaṉ kaṇṇa perumāṉ</l>
<l>cērkkai ceytuta ṉunti yuḷḷē</l>
<l>vāytta ticaimuka ṉintiraṉ vāṉava</l>
<l>rākki ṉāṉṟey vavula kukaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord Kṛṣṇa who is of the nature to guard</l>
<l>the divine worlds, having made a union [with them],</l>
<l>brought into being the celestials, Indra [and]</l>
<l>the four-faced one who was formed inside his navel.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
